Dear Picture Insect fans, we've made BIG improvements in this update. Try the latest version to check out:

- New world map: Discover insects around the world with the new in-app world map.
- Wallpapers: Embrace nature and get refreshed via our eye-opening insect wallpapers.
- Ranking list: Become the world No.1 by identifying more insects.
- Insect Community: Like and commnet on people's snaps in the in-app insect community.

Dear Picture Insect fans, we've made BIG improvements in this update. Try the latest version to check out:

- Higher recognition accuracy: Taking pictures to identify insects is more accurate identification more accurate.
- Clean gallery: Non-insect pictures posted by other users will automatically be filtered out, and more similar insect pictures were added to help users decipher.
- Sample testing picture: new users can now utilize a sample picture to test out how to use the app.

"We've made several improvements in this update. Try the latest version to check out:
- Introduced offline mode, so you can now take photos even if you are not connected to the internet
- Full support Dark Mode to match your system settings
- You can now listen to the pronunciation of the Scientific names
- Grandly introduced Pest Control Guides and Information，keep pests and bugs out with our solutions for pest-free homes!
- New ""People Often Ask"" section on the details page to help you get the answers you want.
- Newly-added ""Use"", ""Interesting Story"" and ""Characteristics"" section on the details page, let's learn more about insect
- Newly-added ""How to identify?"" section helps you identify conveniently"
